# Vendored websearch engine ships its PREBUILT dist/ — a `file:` install on Render can't compile the
# package's TS devDeps, so force-include just that one dist/ (the global `dist/` on line 2 would drop it).
!vendor/websearch/websearch-ts/dist/
!vendor/websearch/websearch-ts/dist/**
packages/*/dist/
packages/*/node_modules/
packages/*/dist-test/
packages/*/package-lock.json
Chat1.md
